Hey.

Ok, first off the original release of this map was never on fpsbanana, this is my very first counter strike map created, my first hammer map. 

Lovely panda uploaded it to og servers and its been played there only.
Ever since the day I made it i've been working on the map on and off, fixing, adding stuff, removing stuff for months. But now I feel like it's ready for release and i'll put it on fpsbanana this time, I hope you will have as much pleasure playing it as I had making it.

peace
